narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take this course if you wish to be exposed to various forms of non-academic writing, and/or explore your own capabilities as a writer.
Million percent yes. This was my favorite class of the semester. Not only does it help you become a better writer, but it relaxed and enjoyable.
I would recommend it - it does help with improving one's writing, but you definitely have to be open to criticism.
Interesting take on "creative" writing--diverges from the standard of academic papers and gives you a new level of freedom in your writing.
English 120 is a great English class that I can recommend wholeheartedly. Not a ton of work, interesting, and useful for improving your writing.

I would absolutely recommend English 120 to another student. One gets to read great writing, and work on your own craft. The class focuses on the writing process itself; English 114 is more research oriented.
